hadiths[106]{hadithnumber,text}:
3555,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke do aadmi muqadma lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to un mein se eik ne arz kya, hamarey darmiyan Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla farmaeyn, aur doosrey ne arz kya : ji haan , Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey darmiyan Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla farmaain aur mujhey baat karney ki ijazat farmaeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' baat karo.'' usney arz kya : mera beta is shakhs ke yahan mazdoor tha, isney iski ehliya ke sath zina kar liya to unhon (yani baaz logon ( ne mujhey bataya ke merey bete par rajm (sangsar) ( ki saza laagu hoti ( hai, lekin maine uskey fidye mein so bakriyan aur apni eik londi de-di, phir maine ehle ilm se masla puchha to unhoney mujhey bataya ke merey bete par so kodey aur saal ki jala watni (ki saza) hai, aur uski ehliya par rajm (sangsar) hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! main tumharey darmiyan Allah ki kitab ke mutabiq faisla karunga , rahi tumhari bakriyan aur tumhari londi wo tumhen wapis mil jaeyngi, raha tumhara beta to is par so kodey aur saal ki jala watni hai aur Unes ! tum us aurat ke paas jaao , agar wo aetraaf jurm kar ley to usey rajm (sangsar) kar do .'' usney aetraaf kar liya to unhoney usey rajm (sangsar) kar diya. muttafaq aleh."
3556,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kunwaarey zaani ke mutalliq so kodey aur saal ki jala watni ka hukm farmatey huey suna . Bukhari ."
3557,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Allah ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja, aur aap par kitab nazil farmaai, Allah Taala ne jo nazil farmaya, is mein aayate-rajm (sangsar) bhi thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rajm (sangsar) kya aur aap ke baad ham ne bhi rajm (sangsar) kya, aur jab shaadi shuda mard aur aurat zina karey to usey rajm (sangsar) karna Allah ki kitab se Sabit hai. b-sharte-ke gawahi Sabit ho jaey ya hamal wazeh ho jaey ya aetraaf jurm ho jaey. muttafaq aleh."
3558,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' (zina ki saza ke mutalliq) mujh se ehkam ki baabat maloomat ley lo . mujh se ehkam ki baabat maloomat ley lo , Allah Taala ne unke liye ( had ( muqarrar kar di, kunwara, kanwari ke sath zina karey to uski had so kodey aur saal ki jala watni hai, aur shaadi shuda, shaadi shuda se zina karey to uski saza so kodey aur rajm (sangsar) hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3559,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke yahood , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney aap ko bataya ke unke eik mard aur eik aurat ne zina kya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : ''tum rajm (sangsar) ke mutalliq Torah mein kya paatey ho ?'' unhoney arz kya : ham unhen zaleel w ruswa kartey hain aur unhen kodey maarey jatey hain, Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tum ne jhoot kaha hai. is main to rajm (sangsar) (ka hukm ( hai. wo Torah laye aur usey khola to un mein se eik ne aayat rajm (sangsar) par apna haath rakh diya aur us se pehley aur uskey baad wala hissey padh diya, Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : apna haath uthao. usney ( haath ( uthaya to is mein aayat rajm (sangsar) thi, unhoney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! us ( Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu)) ne sach kaha, is mein aayat rajm (sangsar) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un dono ke mutalliq hukm farmaya to unhen rajm (sangsar) kar diya gaya. dusri riwayat mein hai : unhoney kaha : apna haath uthao, usney utha liya to is mein aayate-rajm (sangsar) khub wazeh nazar aa rahi thi, usney kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is mein aayat rajm (sangsar) hai lekin ham usey aapas mein chupatey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke mutalliq hukm farmaya to unhen rajm (sangsar) kya gaya. muttafaq aleh."
3560,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif farma they ke eik aadmi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aawaz detey huey kaha : Allah ke Rasool! maine zina kya hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se munh pher liya, to usney dusri taraf se ho kar phir arz kya, maine zina kya hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir us se munh pher liya , jab usney chaar baar gawahi di to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey bula kar farmaya : ''kya tum deewaney ho?'' usney arz kya : nahin ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum shaadi shuda ho ?'' usney arz kya : ji haan , Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey ley jaao aur rajm (sangsar) kar do .'' ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey us shakhs ne bataya jisney Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna ke ham ne us shakhs ko Madina mein rajm (sangsar) kya, jab usey pathar lagey to wo bhag utha yahan tak ke ham ne Madina ke do pahadon ke darmiyan pathreeley ilaqey mein usey ja liya to ham ne usey rajm (sangsar) kya yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaya. aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) Bukhari ki riwayat mein '' , usney arz kya, ji haan '' ke baad hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey janaaz-gaah mein rajm (sangsar) kya gaya, jab usey pathar lagey to wo bhag utha , usey pakad liya gaya aur usey rajm (sangsar) kya gaya yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq kalma khair farmaya aur uski Namaz janaza padhi . muttafaq aleh."
3561,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Maaiz bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''shayad ke tumne bosa liya ho, ya haath lagaya ho ya dekha ho.'' usney arz kya : nahin, Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne us se jima kya?'' aapney kinaaye se baat nahin ki, usney arz kya : ji haan! tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey rajm (sangsar) karney ka hukm farmaya. Bukhari ."
3562,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Maaiz bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mujhey paak kar den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujh par afsos hai, wapis jaao aur Allah se maghfirat talab karo aur uskey huzur tauba karo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, wo thodi der baad wapis aaya aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mujhey paak kar den, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir isi tarah farmaya yahan tak ke jab usney chauthi martaba wohi jumla kaha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''main kis chiz se tumhen paak kar dun?'' usney arz kya : zina (ke gunah) sey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya usey jinon hai? '' aap ko bataya gaya ke usey jinon nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya usney sharab pi hai? '' eik aadmi khada hua aur usney uskey munh se sharab ki boo sunghi to usney us se sharab ki bu na pai phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne zina kya hai? '' usney arz kya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey rajm (sangsar) kya gaya, uskey baad Sahaba do ya teen din (us maamle mein) khamosh rahey phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''Maaiz bin Malik ke barey mein maghfirat talab karo. usney aisi tauba ki hai ke agar usey eik jamaat ke darmiyan taqseem kar diya jaey to wo unke liye kafi ho jaey.'' phir qabila ghaamid ki shaakh Azd se eik aurat aai to usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mujhey paak kar den, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tujh par afsos hai chali jaao, Allah se maghfirat talab karo aur Allah ke huzur tauba karo.'' usney arz kya : aap mujhey wesay hi wapis karna chahtey hain, jaisey aapney Maaiz bin Malik ko wapis kar diya tha, main to zina se hamila ho chuki hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha ke kya : ''tu (hamila) hai? '' usney arz kya : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : '' waza' hamal tak ruki reh.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, ansaar mein se eik aadmi ne uski kafalat ki, yahan tak ke usney bachey ko janm diya to wo ( Ansari ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney arz kya, ghaamdiya ne bachey ko janm dey diya hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tab ham usey rajm (sangsar) nahin karengey , aur ham uskey chhotey se bachey ko chhod den jabkey uskey doodh pilaney ka intizam karney wala bhi koi nahin?'' phir ansaar mein se eik aadmi khada hua aur usney arz kya, Allah ke Nabi ! uska dood pilana merey zimma hai, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey rajm (sangsar) kya. eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''tum jaao yahan tak ke tum bachey ko janm do .'' jab usney bachey ko janm diya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chali jaao aur usey doodh chudaney ki muddat tak usey doodh pilaao.'' jab usney uska doodh chhudaaya to wo bachchey ko lekar aap ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur bachchey ke haath mein roti ka tukda tha, usney arz kya : Allah ke nabi! ye dekhen maine uska doodh chuda diya hai aur ye khana khaney laga hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bachcha kisi musalman shakhs ke hawaley kya, phir uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to uskey seeney ke barabar gaddha khoda gaya, aur aapney logon ko hukm farmaya to unhoney usey rajm (sangsar) kya. Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) eik pathar lekar aaye aur uskey sar par maara jissey khoon ka chheenta unke chehrey par pada to unhoney usey bura-bhala kaha, jis par Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Khalid! thehrao, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! usney aisi tauba ki hai, ke agar mahsoor leney wala aisi tauba karey to uski bhi maghfirat ho jaey.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya aur uski Namaz janaza khud padhaai aur usey dafn kar diya gaya. rawahu Muslim."
3563,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jab tum mein se kisi ki londi zina karey aur uska zina karna wazeh ho jaey to wo is par had qaaim karey aur usey aar na dilaaey, phir agar wo zina karey to wo is par had qaaim karey aur usey aar na dilaaey, phir agar wo teesri martaba zina karey to wo usey bech dey chahey baalon ki rassi ke iwaz bechnaa padey.'' muttafaq aleh."
3564,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : logo! apney ghulamon par had qaaim karo, chahey wo shaadi-shuda hon ya ghair shaadi-shuda, kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik londi ne zina kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm farmaya ke main usey kodey maarun, wo zachgi ke ibtidaai (shuruati) ayyam mein thi, mujhey andesha hua ke agar maine usey kodey maarey to main usey qatl kar dunga, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne achcha kya.'' aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey chhod do yahan tak ke uska khoon band ho jaey, phir is par had qaaim karo aur apney ghulamon par hudood qaaim kya karo.'' rawahu Muslim w Abu-Dawood ."
3565,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Maaiz Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney arz kya ke usney zina kya hai, aapney us se munh pher liya, phir wo dusri taraf se aaya aur arz kya, ke usney zina kya hai, aapney phir us se munh pher liya to wo dusri janib se aa gaya aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! usney zina kya hai, chauthi martaba aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya : aur usey Harra ( Madina ke do pahadon ke darmiyan pathreeli jagah ( ki taraf ley jaya gaya wahan usey patharon se rajm (sangsar) kar diya gaya, jab usney pathar lagney ki takleef mehsus ki to wo tezi se bhag khada hua yahan tak ke wo eik aadmi ke paas se guzra jiskey paas oont ke jabdey ki haddi thi to usney wo usey de maari aur log bhi usey maarney lagey yahan tak ke wo faut ho gaya, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska tazkira kya ke jab usney patharon ki takleef aur maut mehsus ki to wo bhag utha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne usey chhod kyon na diya?'' aur eik riwayat mein hai : ''tum ne usey chhod kyon na diya shayad ke wo tauba kar leta to Allah uski tauba qubul farma leta.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3566,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Maaiz bin Malik se farmaya : '' tumharey mutalliq jo baat mujhey pahunchi hai kya wo durust hai? '' usney arz kya : aap ko merey mutalliq kya baat pahunchi hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke tum ne aal falan ki londi se zina kya hai.'' usney chaar baar iqrar kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey rajm (sangsar) kar diya gaya. rawahu Muslim .
3567,"Hazrat Yazid bin Nuem apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Maaiz (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki mojudgi mein chaar baar iqrar kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey rajm (sangsar) karney ka hukm farmaya , aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hazzal se farmaya : agar tum uski parda poshi kartey to tumharey liye behtar hota .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood. ibne-Munkadir ne farmaya ke Hazzal ne Maaiz (Raziallahu anhu) ko mashwara diya tha ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaey aur aap ko) ye waqia ( bataey ."
3568,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hudood ko baham (aapas mein) maaf kar diya karo, jab maamla mujh tak pahunch gaya to phir had wajib ho gaee.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3569,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''achi sifaat se muttasif logon se hudood ke ilawa unki laghzishon se darguzar kya karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
3570,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis qadr ho sakey musalman se hudood (sazaaon ko) door rakho, agar koi bachaaw ki raah nikalti ho to uski raah chhod do, kyonkey Imam ka darguzar karney mein ghalati karna, saza deney mein ghalati karney se behtar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : ye riwayat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki gaee hai aur uska marfoo na hona ziyada sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3571,"Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik aurat se zina bil-jabr kya gaya to aapney is par had qaaim na ki balke us se ziyadti karney waley par had qaaim ki. raawi ne zikr nahin kya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey liye mehar muqarrar kya ya ke nahin. zaeef rawahu Tirmizi."
3572,"Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur main eik aurat Namaz padhney ke liye nikli to eik aadmi usey mila aur usney usey dhanp liya aur zabardasti us se zina kar liya , usney shor machaya to wo chala gaya, itney mein muhajrin ki eik jamaat guzri to us ( aurat ( ne kaha : falan shakhs ne is-is tarah merey sath kya hai, unhoney us aadmi ko pakda aur usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ley aaye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us aurat se farmaya : ''tum jaao Allah ne tumhen bakhsh diya .'' aur uskey sath zina karney waley shakhs ke mutalliq farmaya : ''usey rajm (sangsar) kar do .'' aur farmaya : '' us shakhs ne aisi tauba ki hai ke agar aisi tauba ehle Madina kartey to wo unki taraf se qubul ho jati .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
3573,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne kisi aurat ke sath zina kya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey kodey maarey gaey, phir aap ko bataya gaya ke wo to shaadi shuda hai to phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey rajm (sangsar) kya gaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3574,"Hazrat Saeed bin Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik aisey shakhs ko laye jo qabiley mein naqisul-khilqat (hijda) aur mareez tha lekin wo unki laundiyon mein se kisi londi ke sath zina karta hua paya gaya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uskey liye khajoor ki eik tehni lo jis mein so shaakhen hun aur phir usey eik hi martaba maaro .'' Sharahus-sunnah , aur ibne-Maja ki riwayat mein isi tarah hai. ( rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah w ibne-Maja ( ."
3575,"Hazrat Ikrima , ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum jis shakhs ko qome-Loot ka sa kaam kartey huey dekho to faail aur maf'ool dono ko qatl kar do.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3576,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs chopaey ke sath bura kaam karey to us shakhs ko qatl kar do aur uskey sath us (chopaey) ko bhi qatl kar do.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se arz kya gaya, chopaey ko kis liye? unhoney kaha : maine is barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kuch nahin suna lekin mera khayal hai ke aapney aisey janwer ka gosht khaney ya us se faeyda uthaney ko napasand farmaya jiskey sath ye kaam kya gaya ho. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja."
3577,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey apni ummat ke mutalliq qome-Loot ke amal mein mulawwis honey ka sab se ziyada andesha hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3578,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke banu-bakr bin Leis qabiley ka eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney eik aurat ke sath zina karney ka chaar baar iqrar kya to aapney usey so kodey maarey , kyonkey wo kunwaaraa tha, phir aapney us shakhs se aurat ke khilaf gawah talab kiye , ( jab wo us se aajiz aa gaya ( to us aurat ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ki qism ! usney jhoot kaha hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is par hade-qazaf (assi kodey saza) qaaim ki . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3579,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab meri bara-at ke barey mein aayaat nazil huin to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par khadey huey to usko zikr farmaya , jab aap member se utrey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do mardon aur eik aurat ke barey mein hukm farmaya to un par had qaaim ki gaee . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3580,Hazrat Naafe se riwayat hai ke) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya ( Safiya binte-abi Ubaid ne usey bataya ke amaarat ke ghulamon mein se eik ghulam ne khums ki eik londi se zina bil-jabr kya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us ghulam ko kodey maarey aur londi ko kodey na maarey kyonkey usney usey majbur kya tha. Bukhari.
3581,"Hazrat Yazid bin Nueim bin Hazzal apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Maaiz bin Malik yateem they aur merey walid ki kafalat mein they, unhoney qabiley ki eik londi se zina kya to merey walid ne unhen kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaao aur apni harkat ke mutalliq unhen bataao shayad ke wo tumharey liye maghfirat talab karen, unka maqsad ye tha ke shayad uskey liye najat ki koi sabeel nikal aaye , wo aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine zina ka irtikab kya hai aap mujh par Allah ki kitab (ka hukm ( qaaim karen, aapney us se aeraz farmaya to wo dobara aaya aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! maine zina kya hai. aap mujh par Allah ki kitab (ka hukm ( qaaim karen, ( wo kehta raha ( yahan tak ke usney chaar martaba aisey kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne chaar martaba ye baat ki hai, bataao tum ne kis ke sath ( zina kya hai) ?'' usney arz kya : falan aurat ke sath , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya to uskey sath ham bistar hua ?'' usney arz kya : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne uskey sath milaap kya ?'' usney arz kya : ji haan : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne us se jima (sambhog) kya?'' usney arz kya, ji haan, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya ke usey rajm (sangsar) kya jaey, usey Harra ki taraf ley jaya gaya, jab usney patharon ki takleef mehsus ki to wo bardasht na kar saka to wo (rajm (sangsar) ki jagah sey) bhag khada hua . lekin Abdullah bin Unais ne usey ja liya jabkey uskey deegar saathi peechey reh gaey unhoney oont ki pindli ki haddi usey maari aur qatl kar diya, phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur aap ko uskey mutalliq bataya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne usey chhod kyon na diya shayad ke wo tauba kar leta aur Allah uski tauba qubul farma leta.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3582,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis qom mein zina aam ho jata hai wo qehat saali ka shikar ho jati hai, aur jis qom mein rishwat aam ho jaey is par khof musallat kar diya jata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3583,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs qome-Loot ka sa amal karey wo maloon hai.'' rawahu rizeen .
3584,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dono (karney waley aur karaney waley) ko jala diya, jabkey abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne un dono par deewar gira di."
3585,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall us aadmi ki taraf ( nazar rehmat sey) nahin dekhta jo kisi mard ke sath bura kaam karey ya wo aurat ki peeth mein bura kaam karey.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
3586,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney farmaya : jo shakhs kisi chopaey ke sath bura kaam karey to is par koi had nahin .'' Imam Tirmizi ne Sufiyan Sauri se riwayat kya ke unhoney kaha : ye hadees , hadees awwal : ''jo shakhs kisi chopaey ke sath bura kaam karey to usey qatl kar do .'' se ziyada sahih hai. aur ehle ilm ke yahan usi par amal hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
3587,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her qarib w baeed (nasab ke lihaz se yaqoot ke lihaz sey) par Allah ki hudood nafiz kar do. aur Allah ke (hukm jari kerney) mein kisi malamat gar ki malamat tumharey aadey na aaye.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
3588,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki hadon mein se kisi had ka qaaim kar dena, Allah ke shehron par chaalis raaten barish honey se behtar hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
3589,Hazrat Imam Nasai ne usey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Nasai.
3590,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chothai Dinar ya usse ziyada (maaliyat ki chori ( par chor ka haath kaata jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
3591,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen dirham maaliyat ki dhaal ki chori par chor ka haath kaata. muttafaq aleh."
3592,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah chor par lanat karey ke wo andaa churata hai to uska haath kaat diya jata hai, aur wo rassi churata hai to uska haath kaat diya jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3593,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' darkht par lagey huey phal aur shigoofey mein haath nahin kaata jaeyga.'' rawahu Malik w Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w Darmi w ibne-Maja."
3594,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya ke aap se darakhton par lagey huey phal (ki chori) ke barey mein puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney usey godaam mein mehfooz kar leney ke baad chori kya aur wo dhaal ki qeemat ko pahunch gaya to phir is par qata' ( haath kaatna ( hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3595,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman bin abi Husain Makki se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''na latkey huey phalon ( ki chori ( mein qata (hath kata jana) hai na pahad ke daman mein charney waley janwer (ki chori) mein, jab wo ( janwer ( baadey mein panah guzeen hon aur phal godaam mein mehfooz ho to phir uski chori par qata hai jab wo dhaal ki qeemat ko pahunch jaey.'' rawahu Malik."
3596,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''daaku par qata ( haath kaatna ( nahin (us ki saza alag hai) , aur jo shakhs badey-badey daakey daley wo ham mein se nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3597,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khayanat karney waley, daaka dalney waley aur jhapat kar maal hasil karney waley par ''qata'' nahin .'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
3598,"aur Sharahus-sunnah mein marwi (bayan) hai ke Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) Madina aaye to wo apni chadar ka sarhana bana kar masjid mein so gaey, eik chor aaya aur usney unki chadar pakad li to unhoney usey giraftar kar liya, aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaye, aapney uska haath kaatney ka hukm farmaya to Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, maine us (qata) ka irada nahin kya tha, wo ( chadar (us ( chor ( par sadqa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne usey merey paas laney se pehley kyon na maaf kar diya.'' (rawahu al-baghwi fi Sharahus-sunnah)."
3599,Hazrat Imam ibne-Maja ne isi tarah Abdullah bin Safwan an (an) ابیہ ki sanad se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja .
3600,aur Imam Darmi ne ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Darmi .
3601,"Hazrat Basr bin Irtaat bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''ghazwe mein haath na kaatey jaeyn.'' albatta Imam Abu-Dawood aur Imam Nasai ne ghazwe ke bajaey ''safar'' ka lafz istimal kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Darmi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3602,"Hazrat abu-Salma, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chor ke barey mein farmaya : ''agar wo chori karey to uska haath kaat do, agar phir chori karey to uska paaon kaat do, agar phir chori karey to uska (doosra) haath kaat do aur agar phir chori karey to uska ( doosra) paaon kaat do.'' mauzu, ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
3603,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik chor Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uska haath kaat do .'' uska haath kaat diya gaya. phir usey (doosri chori mein) dusri martaba pesh kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uska haath kaat do.'' uska haath kaat diya gaya, phir usey teesri martaba pesh kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uska paaon kaat do.'' uska paaon kaat diya gaya, phir chauthi martaba pesh kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uska paaon kaat do .'' uska paaon kaat diya gaya, phir usey paanchwen martaba laya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey qatl kar do .'' ham usey ley gaey aur usey qatl kar diya. phir ham ne usey ghaseet kar kunwen mein phenk diya aur is par pathar dal diye . rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
3604,"aur unhoney Sharahus-sunnah mein chor ke haath kaatney ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us (ke haath) ko kaat do phir usey dagh do.'' ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
3605,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik chor Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya gaya to uska haath kaat diya gaya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey uski gardan mein latka diya gaya. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
3606,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab ghulam chori karey to usey bech do chaahey eik ''nash'' ( bees dirham ( hi miley .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
3607,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik chor Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska haath kaat diya, to unhon ( Sahaba ( ne arz kya, hamara aap ke mutalliq ye guman nahin tha ke aap uskey mutalliq ye kuch karengey , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar (farz kar lijiye) Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) bhi hotin to main (bila tafriq) unka haath bhi kaat-ta.'' rawahu Nasai ."
3608,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi apna ghulam lekar umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to usney kaha : uska haath kaat dalen kyonkey usney meri ehliya ka aaina chura liya hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : is par qata nahin aur wo tumhara khaadim hai, usney tumhara saman utha liya hai. rawahu Malik."
3609,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abu-Zar!'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main hazir hun, isi mein meri saadat hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhari us waqt kya haalat hogi jab log kasrat se maut ka shikar hongey aur us waqt qabr ghulam ke iwaz milegi?'' maine arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum sabr karna.'' Hammad bin abi Suleman (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : kafan chor ka haath kaata jaeyga kyonkey wo maiyat par uskey ghar mein dakhil hua hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3610,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke makhzumiya aurat, jisney chori ki thi, ke waqie ne Qureshiyon ko ghamzada kar diya to unhoney kaha : uskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kon sifarish karey ? phir unhoney kaha : ye kaam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chahetey sirf Usama bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) hi kar saktey hain. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sifarish ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum Allah ki hudood mein se eik had ke barey mein sifarish kartey ho ?'' phir aap khadey huye, khutba irshad farmaya , phir farmaya : ''tum se pehley log sirf isi wajeh se halak kar diye gaey ke jab un mein se khandani shakhs chori karta to wo usey chhod detey aur jab kamzor shakhs chori karta to wo is par had qaaim kar detey , Allah ki qism ! agar Fatima binte-Muhammad (Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki beti Fatima (Raziallahu anhu)) bhi chori kartin to main unka haath bhi kaat deta.'' Bukhari , Muslim . aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya : eik makhzoomiya aurat ( Fatima bint Aswad) thi jo udhar chizen liya karti thi aur phir unki wapsi ka inkar kar diya karti thi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska haath kaatney ka hukm farmaya to uskey khandan waley Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye aur unhoney un se baat ki aur Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne uskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sifarish ki, phir Imam Muslim ne hadees mazkura ke mutabiq hadees bayan ki. muttafaq aleh."
3611,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ki sifarish Allah ki hadon mein se kisi had ke lagun karney mein rukawat ho gaee to usney Allah ki mukhalifat ki, jisney jantey huey kisi batil ( nahaq (ke barey mein jhagda kya to wo us se door honey tak Allah Taala ki narazi mein rehta hai aur jisney kisi momin par bohtan lagaya to wo kach-lahu ke keechad mein rahega yahan tak ke wo us se nikal aaye jo usney kaha hai.'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, aur Behaqi ki Shobil-emaan main eik riwayat hai : ''jisney kisi jhagdey par iaanat ki jabkey wo nahin janta ke wo haq hai ya batil to wo Allah ki narazi mein rehta hai yahan tak ke wo us se door ho jaey.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w al-Behaqi ."
3612,"Hazrat abu-Umaiya makhzoomi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik chor laya gaya, usney jurm qabool kar liya lekin us se maal baramad na hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''mera khayal hai ke tum ne chori nahin ki.'' usney arz kya, kyon nahin, zarur ki hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do ya teen martaba ye baat dohrai lekin wo her martaba aetraaf karta raha, aapney uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to uska haath kaat diya gaya. aur phir usey aap ke paas laya gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''Allah se maghfirat talab karo aur uskey huzur tauba karo.'' usney arz kya : main Allah se maghfirat talab karta hun aur uskey huzur tauba karta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen baar farmaya : ''aey Allah! iski tauba qubul farma.'' aur maine usoole-arbaa, Jaame al-usool , Shobil-emaan aur muaalim sunan mein abu-Umaiya se isi tarah paya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Dar-Qutni ."
3613,aur masaabeh ke nuskhon mein '' abu-Umaiya '' ki bajaey '' abu-Ramsa '' hai. rawahu masaabeh.
3614,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sharab noshi par khajoor ki tehniyan aur jootey maarey aur abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne chaalis kodey maarey. muttafaq aleh.
3615,aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) eik aur hadees mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sharab noshi par chaalis jootey aur shaakhen maara kartey they. rawahu Muslim .
3616,"Hazrat Saaib bin Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke dure-khilaafat aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke khilaafat ke shuru ke daur mein sharab nosh ko laya jata to ham apney haathon, jooton aur apney kapdon ke sath usey maartay they yahan tak ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilaafat ke aakhiri daur mein chaalis kodey maarey jatey they yahan tak ke jab wo had se badh gaey aur sarkashi par utar aaye to unhoney assi kodey maarey. Bukhari ."
3617,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs sharab piye to usey kodey maaro , agar wo chauthi martaba piye to usey qatl kar do.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir uskey baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik aadmi pesh kya gaya jisney chauthi martaba sharab pi thi aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey qatl nahin kya. rawahu Tirmizi."
3618,Hazrat Imam Abu-Dawood ne usey Qabisa bin Zueb se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood .
3619,"Hazrat Abu-Dawood aur Tirmizi ki dusri riwayat aur Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi ki Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ki jamaat , jin mein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) , Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) aur shareed (Raziallahu anhu) hain, se ''usey qatl kar do.'' tak marwi (bayan) hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja w Darmi ."
3620,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, goya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekh raha hun jab eik shakhs ko, jisney sharab pi rakhi thi, laya gaya to aapney logon se farmaya : ''usey maaro.'' un mein se kisi ne usey jooton ke sath maara, kisi ne lathi ke sath maara aur kisi ne usey khajoor ki sabz (hara) shaakh ke sath maara, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zamin se khaak uthai aur uskey chehrey par dey maari . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3621,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik aadmi laya gaya jisney sharab pi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey maaro.'' ham mein se koi usey haath maar raha tha, koi apney kapdey se aur koi apney jootey se maar raha tha phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey malamat karo.'' wo uski taraf mutawajjeh ho kar kehney lagey : to Allah se na dara, tujhey Allah ka khof na aaya aur tujhey Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se haya na aai, aur kisi ne keh diya : Allah tumhen ruswa karey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is tarah na kaho, aur uskey khilaf shetan ki madad na karo. balke tum kaho : aey Allah ! usey bakhsh dey aur is par rehem farma .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3622,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne sharab pi to wo madhosh ho gaya. wo raastey mein jhoomta hua mila to usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf ley jaya janey laga. jab wo Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ke barabar pahuncha to wo bhag kar Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas pahunch gaya aur un se chimat gaya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uska zikr kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) muskura diye , aur farmaya : ''kya usney ye kya ?'' aur aapney uskey mutalliq kuch bhi na kaha . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3623,"Hazrat Umer bin Saeed Nakhai bayan kartey hain, maine Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huey suna : agar main kisi shakhs par had qaaim karun aur wo faut ho jaey to main apney dil mein kisi qism ka afsos nahin karunga. lekin agar shraabi par had qaaim karun aur wo faut ho jaey to main uski taraf se diyat dunga. ye isliye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is barey mein koi had (saza) muqarrar nahin farmaai. muttafaq aleh."
3624,"Hazrat Saur bin Zaid dailmi bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne sharab ki saza ke mutalliq mashwara talab kya to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen farmaya : mera khayal hai ke aap (Raziallahu anhu) usey assi kodey maaren, kyonkey jab wo sharab peeta hai to wo madhosh ho jata hai aur jab madhosh ho jata hai to wo hiziyaani keyfiyat mein aul-faul baaten karta hai. aur jab wo aul-faul baaten karta hai to phir iftna pardazi karta hai, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne sharab ki had mein assi kodey maarey. rawahu Malik."
3625,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi jiska naam Abdullah aur laqab himaar tha, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hansaaya karta tha, jabkey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sharab-noshi ke jurm mein is par had nafiz ki thi, eik roz usey pesh kya gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey kodey maarney ka hukm farmaya to usey kodey maarey gaey, logon mein se kisi ne keh diya, aey Allah is par lanat farma, kitni hi baar usey (sharab noshi ke jurm mein) laya ja chuka hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''us par lanat na bhejo, Allah ki qasam! main jo janta hun wo ye hai ke wo Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mohabbat karta hai.'' Bukhari ."
3626,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik aadmi laya gaya jisney pi rakhi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey maaro.'' ham mein se koi apney haath se maarney wala tha, koi jooton ke sath aur koi apney kapdey ke sath maarney wala tha, jab wo wapis hua to kisi ne keh diya : Allah tumhen ruswa karey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aisey na kaho , uskey khilaf shetan ki madad na karo.'' Bukhari ."
3627,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Aslami ( Maaiz (Raziallahu anhu)) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur apni zaat ke khilaf chaar martaba gawahi di ke usney eik aurat ke sath haram kaam ( zina (ka irtikab kya hai. aap her martaba us se munh phertey rahey, paanchwen martaba aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tawajjoh farmaai to puchha : ''kya tum ne us se jima kya hai? '' usney arz kya : ji haan, farmaya : '' yahan tak ke tumhari ye chiz ( sharm-gah (us aurat ki us chiz ( sharm-gah ( mein gum ho gaee .'' usney arz kya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis tarah salaai surmey daani mein aur rassi kunwen mein dakhil ho ( kar ghayeb ho ( jati hai? '' usney arz kya : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho zina kya hai? '' usney arz kya : ji haan , maine uskey sath haram taur par wo kaam kya hai jo aadmi halal taur par apni ehliya ke sath karta hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney is qol w iqrar se kya chahtey ho?'' usney arz kya : main chahta hun ke aap mujhey paak farma den, aapney uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey rajm (sangsar) kar diya gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney Sahaba mein se do aadmiyon ko suna ke un mein se eik apney sathi se keh raha tha is aadmi ko dekho jiski Allah ne sattar poshi ki thi, uskey nafs ne usey na chhoda yahan tak ke wo kuttey ki tarah sangsaar kar diya gaya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unke mutalliq khamoshi ikhtiyar farmaai, phir kuch der chaley yahan tak ke aap eik murdar gadhey ke paas se guzrey jisney apni taang utha rakhi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' falan falan shakhs kahan hain ?'' un dono ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! ham hazir hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dono nichey utro aur us murdar gadhey ka gosht khaao .'' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Nabi ! usey kon khayega ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne abhi jo apney bhai ki izzat kharab ki wo usey khaney se bhi ziyada sangeen hai, us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai! wo to ab jannat ki nehron mein ghota zani kar raha hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
3628,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne koi gunah kya aur us gunah ki had qaaim kar di gaee to wo ( had ( uska kaffara bin jati hai.'' (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
3629,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne saza wajib ho chuka koi gunah kya aur usey duniya mein uski saza mil gaee to Allah us se ziyada aadil hai ke wo apney bandey ko aakhirat mein dobara saza dey , aur jo shakhs saza wakon ho jaaney wala koi gunah karey aur Allah uski parda poshi farmaai aur us se darguzar farmaai to Allah us se ziyada karim hai ke wo kisi chiz par pakad karey jisse usney darguzar farmaya ho.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
3630,"Hazrat abu-Barda bin Niyar (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki hudood mein se kisi had ke siwa das kodon se ziyada na maarey jaeyn .'' muttafaq aleh."
3631,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi maarey to wo chehrey ( par maarney ( se bachey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3632,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab aadmi kisi ( musalman ( aadmi se kahey : aey yahudi! to usey bees kodey maaro, aur jab kahey : aey hijdey! to usey bees kodey maaro aur jo shakhs kisi Mohrim khatoon se jima karey to usey qatl kar do.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
3633,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum aisa aadmi paao jisney Allah ki raah (maal ghanimat) mein khayanat ki ho to uska saman jala do aur usey maaro.'' Tirmizi . Abu-Dawood . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood .
3634,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sharab un darakhton khajoor aur angoor se tayyar hoti hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3635,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke member par khutba diya to farmaya : sharab ki hurmat nazil ho chuki, aur wo paanch ashiya : angoor, khajoor, gehun, jo aur shehad se tayyar hoti hai, aur sharab wo hai jo aql par parda dal dey. Bukhari ."
3636,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab sharab haram ki gaee, ham anguron ki sharab kam paatey they, aur hamari ziyada tar sharab khushk aur taza khajoor se tayyar hoti thi. Bukhari."
3637,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se shehad ki nabeez ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her nasha aawar mashrub haram hai.'' muttafaq aleh."
3638,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her nasha-aawar chiz sharab hai aur her nasha aawar chiz haram hai. jis shakhs ne duniya mein sharab pi aur wo usi par dawaam kartey huey tauba kiye baghair faut ho jaey to wo usey aakhirat mein nahin piyega.'' rawahu Muslim."
3639,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Yamen se eik aadmi aaya to usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey, apney mulk mein Juwar se tayyar honey wali Muzar naami pi janey wali sharab ke mutalliq puchha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wo nasha aawar hai? '' usney arz kya : ji haan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her nasha aawar chiz haram hai. be-shak ye baat Allah ke zimme hai ke jo shakhs nasha aawar chiz piyega to Allah usey (teenatul-Khabaal) palaeyga.'' Sahaba kiram ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! (teenatul-khabal) kya chiz hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jahannamiyon ka paseena ya jahannamiyon ke zakhmon se behney wala khoon aur peep.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3640,"Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne taza khajoor aur khushk khajoor ko milaaney, Munaqqa aur taza khajoor ko milaaney aur kachchi khajoor aur taza khajoor milaaney se mana farmaya, aur farmaya : ''un mein se her eik ki alag-alag nabeez tayyar karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
3641,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sharab se sirka bananey ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin.'' rawahu Muslim.
3642,"Hazrat Waayel Hizrami se riwayat hai ke Tariq bin Suwed ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sharab ke barey mein puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen mana farma diya, unhoney arz kiya : main usey dawaai ke liye banata hun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo dawaai nahin, wo to bimari hai.'' rawahu Muslim."
3643,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs sharab peeta hai to Allah chaalis roz tak uski Namaz qubul nahin karta , agar wo tauba kar ley to Allah uski tauba qubul kar leta hai, agar wo dobara pi ley to Allah chaalis roz tak uski Namaz qubul nahin karta , agar wo tauba kar ley to Allah uski tauba qubul kar leta hai, agar wo teesri baar pi ley to Allah uski chaalis roz tak Namaz qubul nahin karta , agar wo tauba kar ley to Allah uski tauba qubul kar leta hai, agar wo chauthi martaba pi ley to Allah uski chaalis roz tak Namaz qubul nahin karta, agar wo tauba karey to Allah uski tauba qubul nahin karta , aur wo usey jahannamiyon ke peep ki nehar se palaey ga.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3644,"Hazrat Imam Nasai , ibne-Maja aur Imam Darmi ne usey Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. rawahu Nasai, ibne-Maja aur Darmi."
3645,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis chiz ki Kasir (ziyada) miqdaar nasha aawar ho to uski qaleel (kam) miqdaar bhi haram hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3646,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab farq (sau-ratl) nasha aawar ho to uska chullu-bhar peena bhi haram hai.'' rawahu Ahmed, Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3647,"Hazrat Noman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gehun se sharab hoti hai, jo se sharab hoti hai. khajoor se sharab hoti hai, angoor se bhi aur shehad se bhi sharab hoti hai.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
3648,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, hamarey paas eik yateem bachchey ki sharab thi, jab Sura Maeyda nazil hui to maine uskey mutalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha aur maine arz kiya, wo yateem ki hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey baha do.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
3649,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) , Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney arz kiya : Allah ke Nabi ! maine apney zere-parwarish yateem bachchon ke liye sharab khareedi hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sharab baha do aur (uskey) bartan tod do.'' Tirmizi. aur unhoney isey zaeef qarar diya, aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yateem bachchon ki wirasat mein aaney wali sharab ke mutalliq puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey baha do.'' unhoney arz kiya : kya main usey sirka na bana lun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
3650,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne her nasha aawar aur quwaa(jism) mein susti paida karney wali her chiz se mana farmaya hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3651,"Hazrat Dailam Himyari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! ham sard ilaqey mein rehtey hain aur wahan mashaqqat wala kaam kartey hain, ham us gehun se sharab tayyar kartey hain jiskey zariey ham apney kaam aur apney ilaqey ki sardi ke muqabley mein quwat hasil kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya wo nasha aawar hai?'' maine arz kiya : ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ius se ijtinab (bacha) karo.'' maine arz kiya : log usey tarak karney waley nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar wo usey na choden to un se ladaai karo.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3652,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sharab, juey, chhotey tabley aur ghubaira (sharab ki eik qism) se mana farmaya, aur farmaya : ''her nasha aawar chiz haram hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
3653,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''waliden ka nafarman , qammaar , ehsan jatlaaney wala aur hamesha sharab peeney wala jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga.'' Darmi. aur unhi ki eik riwayat mein qammaar ke bajaey zina se paida hone wala hai. rawahu Darmi."
3654,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah Taala ne mujhey jahan walon ke liye baaise rehmat aur baaise hidayat bana kar Nabi banakar bheja. aur merey rab ne mosiqi (sangeet) ke aalaat (yantro), buton , saleebon aur rusoommaat jahiliyat khatam karney ka mujhey hukm farmaya aur merey rab ne meri izzat ki qism utha kar farmaya : ''merey jis bandey ne sharab ka eik ghoont piya to main usi jaisi usey peep pilaunga aur jisney merey dar ki wajeh se usey tarak kar diya to main usey sharabe-tahoor pilaunga.'' rawahu Ahmed."
3655,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne teen qism ke logon : hamesha sharab peeney waley, waliden ke nafarman aur devas jo apney ehle w ayaal mein zina barqarar rakhney wala ho, par jannat ko haram qarar dey diya hai.'' rawahu Ahmed w Nasai ."
3656,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen qism ke log : hamesha sharab peeney wala, qata rehmi karney wala aur jadu ka yaqin karney wala, jannat mein nahin jaeyngey.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3657,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sharab noshi par dawaam ikhtiyar karney wala agar (usi haalat mein) faut ho jaey to wo Allah Taala se but ke pujaari ki tarah mulaqat kerega .'' rawahu Ahmed ."
3658,Hazrat Imam ibne-Maja ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja .
3659,"Hazrat Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein Muhammad bin Abdullah an (an) ابیہ ki sanad se riwayat kya hai, aur Imam Behaqi ne kaha : Imam Bukhari ne Muhammad bin Abdullah an (an) ابیہ se tareekh mein zikr kya hai. ( rawahu Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
3660,Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo kaha kartey they : main is baat ki parwah nahin karta ke main sharab pi lun ya Allah ke siwa us sutoon ki puja kar lun . sahih moquf rawahu Nasai .
